data.description: NICE PRICE REDUCTION!! If you have been looking for an opportunity to move to a larger home now is your chance. There has been a lot of special attention paid to the detail and characteristics of this home being updated where the kitchen opens to the great room giving an open flow to the floor plan. The split bedroom design gives privacy to the primary bedroom with its own private ensuite. The second and third bedrooms are on the opposite side and have their own bathroom to share. The hardwood floors are in all of the common areas for ease of cleaning those high traffic areas. Downstairs you will find a large den with wet bar, bedroom and full bath and a nice size two car garage.  With summer around the corner, the pool will be ready to open. This home sits on a nice lot and the backyard is fenced with the pool having its own perimeter fencing. The screened in back porch overlooks the pool where you will enjoy grilling after a day in the pool.
